<inglise> DECISION OF THE REPRESENTATIVES OF THE GOVERNMENTS OF THE MEMBER STATES, MEETING WITHIN THE COUNCIL of 17 June 1999 authorising the Commission to terminate the Agreement of 28 July 1956 on the setting of through international railway tariffs for the carriage of coal and steel in transit through Swiss territory </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGUS KOKKU TULNUD LIIKMESRIIKIDE VALITSUSTE ESINDAJATE OTSUS, millega komisjonil lubatakse l&otilde;petada 28. juuli 1956. aasta leping otseste rahvusvaheliste raudteetariifide kehtestamise kohta s&ouml;e ja terase transiitveo suhtes &Scaron;veitsi territooriumi kaudu 17. juuni 1999 </eesti>
<inglise> (1999/415/ECSC) </inglise>
<eesti> (1999/415/EST&Uuml;) </eesti>
<inglise> THE REPRESENTATIVES OF THE GOVERNMENTS OF THE MEMBER STATES OF THE EUROPEAN COAL AND STEEL COMMUNITY, MEETING WITHIN THE COUNCIL, </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGUS KOKKU TULNUD EUROOPA S&Ouml;E- JA TERASE&Uuml;HENDUSE LIIKMESRIIKIDE VALITSUSTE ESINDAJAD, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Coal and Steel Community, and in particular Article 70 thereof, and to the Convention on the transitional provisions, and in particular Article 10, second and third paragraphs, point 2 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa S&ouml;e- ja Terase&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, eriti selle artiklit 70, ning &uuml;leminekus&auml;tete konventsiooni, eriti selle artikli 10 teise ja kolmanda l&otilde;ike punkti 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Coal and Steel Community, and in particular Article 14 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa S&ouml;e- ja Terase&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, eriti selle artiklit 14, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Agreement of 28 July 1956 on the setting of through international railway tariffs for the carriage of coal and steel in transit through Swiss territory(1), and in particular Article 11 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse 28. juuli 1956. aasta lepingut otseste rahvusvaheliste raudteetariifide kehtestamise kohta s&ouml;e ja terase transiitveo suhtes &Scaron;veitsi territooriumi kaudu, (1) eriti selle artiklit 11, </eesti>
<inglise> (1) Whereas maintaining the Agreement no longer seems economically justified, given that the ECSC 9001 tariffs have been almost entirely replaced by customised contracts between clients and carriers; whereas rail transport rates are based on the rates dictated by other modes of transport, in particular road transport; whereas rail transport market forces and intermodal competition have removed the economic justification for the Agreement; whereas it should also be recalled that Swiss rail operators are not required to apply the ECSC 9001 tariff for transit transport; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: 1) kuna EST&Uuml; 9001 tariifid on peaaegu t&auml;ielikult asendatud klientide ja veoettev&otilde;tjate vaheliste individuaallepingutega, ei tundu lepingu s&auml;ilitamine enam majanduslikult p&otilde;hjendatud; raudteevedude hinnad p&otilde;hinevad teiste transpordiliikide, eelk&otilde;ige maanteetranspordi puhul v&auml;lja kujunenud hindadel; raudteevedude turuj&otilde;ud ja eri transpordiliikide vaheline konkurents on k&otilde;rvaldanud lepingu majanduslikud p&otilde;hjendused; samuti tuleks r&otilde;hutada, et &Scaron;veitsi raudtee-ettev&otilde;tjad ei ole kohustatud kohaldama transiitvedude suhtes EST&Uuml; 9001 tariife; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) Whereas termination of the Agreement by the ECSC Member States would have no economic consequences for Switzerland, since the Swiss railway companies do not apply the ECSC 9001 tariff for the transport of ECSC products in transit, </inglise>
<eesti> 2) lepingu l&otilde;petamine EST&Uuml; liikmesriikide poolt ei too &Scaron;veitsile kaasa majanduslikke tagaj&auml;rgi, sest &Scaron;veitsi raudtee-ettev&otilde;tjad ei kohalda EST&Uuml; 9001 tariife EST&Uuml; toodete transiitvedude suhtes, </eesti>
<inglise> HAVE DECIDED AS FOLLOWS: </inglise>
<eesti> ON KOKKU LEPPINUD J&Auml;RGMISES. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The Commission, acting for the ECSC High Authority, is hereby authorised to terminate the Agreement of 28 July 1956 on the setting of through international railway tariffs for the carriage of coal and steel in transit through Swiss territory, and to inform the Member States, meeting within the Council, of this termination, on behalf of the representatives of the Governments of the ECSC Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevaga antakse komisjonile volitused l&otilde;petada EST&Uuml; &Uuml;lemameti nimel 28. juuli 1956. aasta leping otseste rahvusvaheliste raudteetariifide kehtestamise kohta s&ouml;e ja terase transiitveo suhtes &Scaron;veitsi territooriumi kaudu ning teatada EST&Uuml; liikmesriikide valitsuste esindajate nimel k&otilde;nealuse lepingu l&otilde;petamisest n&otilde;ukogus kokku tulnud liikmesriikidele. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Decision shall enter into force on the day following its adoption. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev otsus j&otilde;ustub selle vastuv&otilde;tmisele j&auml;rgneval p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Luxembourg, 17 June 1999. </inglise>
<eesti> Luxembourg, 17. juuni 1999 </eesti>
<inglise> The President </inglise>
